name: MA6 -2
query:
SELECT sa.cg_utr_number as sa_cg_utr, sa.cg_formatted_utr_number as sa_cg_formatted_utr , sa.claim_id as sa_claim_id ,sa.paid_date as sa_paid_date, tb.name as bill_no FROM tabBill tb, `tabSettlement Advice` sa ,tabMatcher tm
WHERE tm.sales_invoice=tb.name and tm.settlement_advice=sa.name and tm.match_logic in ("MA6-2");
